    "slug": "plug-in-solar-caravans-motorhomes-uk",
    "title": "Plug-in Solar for Caravans, Motorhomes and Campervans UK",
    "excerpt": "Harness solar power for van life without breaking the bank. Flexible panels, battery pairing, and off-grid camping made practical and affordable.",
    "date": "2026-04-13",
    "category": "Location Guides",
