    "title": "Plug-in Solar in London: Urban Installation Guide",
    "excerpt": "London homes face urban shading, conservation areas, and flat roofs. This guide covers balcony installations, terraces, and how to navigate planning rules.",
    "date": "2026-04-13",
    "category": "Location Guides",
