    "title": "Plug-in Solar for Semi-Detached Houses UK: A Practical Guide",
    "excerpt": "Semi-detached homes offer unique advantages for plug-in solar. Learn about side access, shared features, and the best installation approaches.",
    "date": "2026-04-13",
    "category": "Property Guides",
    "market": "uk",
